com.github.robtimus.junit.support

Class OptionalAssertions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.robtimus.junit.support.OptionalAssertions

  • public final class OptionalAssertions
extends Object
    A collection of utility methods that support asserting conditions in tests for Optional, OptionalInt, OptionalLong and OptionalDouble.
    Since:
    2.0
    Author:
    Rob Spoor
